  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Atranta\" title=\"House Vance of Atranta\"><img alt=\"House Vance of Atranta.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/50px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/75px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/100px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Kirth Vance</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Atranta\" title=\"House Vance of Atranta\"><img alt=\"House Vance of Atranta.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/50px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/75px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/100px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Atranta\" title=\"House Vance of Atranta\">House Vance of Atranta</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Norbert_Vance\" title=\"Norbert Vance\">Norbert Vance</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Kirth Vance</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Atranta\" title=\"House Vance of Atranta\">House Vance of Atranta</a> and the fourth son of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Norbert_Vance\" title=\"Norbert Vance\">Norbert Vance</a>. He has four brothers; Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ronald_Vance\" title=\"Ronald Vance\">Ronald</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ellery_Vance\" title=\"Ellery Vance\">Ellery</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Hugo_Vance\" title=\"Hugo Vance\">Hugo</a> and Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Vance\" title=\"Jon Vance\">Jon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Kirth is a good friend of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kirth_Vance&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhov